text: "All Goes Wrong" is a song by British electronic music production duo Chase & Status. It features vocals from Tom Grennan. The song was released as a digital download on 22 September 2016 through MTA Records and Mercury Records.All Goes Wrong (feat. Tom Grennan) - Single by Chase & Status on Apple Music The song peaked to number 65 on the UK Singles Chart. The song was written by Saul Milton, William Kennard, Kieron McIntosh, Nathaniel Ledwidge, Tom Grennan, Dean McIntosh. It was produced by Chase & Status. ==Music video== A music video to accompany the release of "All Goes Wrong" was first released onto YouTube on 12 July 2016. It had a total length of 3:32.Chase & Status - All Goes Wrong ft. Tom Grennan - YouTube ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2016 songs
